OL,3,CKing Charles visits Scottish Borders
OL,4,Ctown of Jedburgh
OL,6,FKing Charles has been back in the
OL,7,FScottish Borders to visit Jedburgh,
OL,8,Fwhere he took part in a centuries old
OL,9,Fgame of hand ba'.
OL,11,FThe King arrived by helicopter this
OL,12,Fmorning, first meeting with
OL,13,Findependent traders at the local
OL,14,Fmarket.
OL,16,FHis Majesty was greeted by school
OL,17,Fchildren against a backdrop of live
OL,18,Fmusic and performance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
