OL,3,CKing Charles visits Scottish Borders
OL,4,Ctown of Jedburgh
OL,6,FThe Monarch spoke to stallholders from
OL,7,Fthe local community before walking to
OL,8,Fthe Jam Shed, which provides a space
OL,9,Ffor members to create, share skills
OL,10,Fand build connections.
OL,12,FIt features carpentry workshops and a
OL,13,Fsocial area to display handmade gifts.
OL,15,FThe King's visit was timed to take
OL,16,Fplace during Jedburgh's festival,
OL,17,Fwhich runs for two weeks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
