OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1783691326
OL,3,CKing Charles visits Scottish Borders
OL,4,Ctown of Jedburgh
OL,6,FMs Hackney said: "He said to me his
OL,7,Fnanny in the 1940s was from Jedburgh
OL,8,Fand he just met her nephew at the
OL,9,Fmen's shed, who gave him some Jethart
OL,10,Fsnails sweets as well. And apparently
OL,11,Fthe nanny used to bring him the snails
OL,12,Fwhen he was a child."
OL,14,FKing Charles left Jedburgh by
OL,15,Fhelicopter mid-afternoon.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
